review 2:
Support this little amazing place!
It is a little coffee and food place located in the middle of jungle and coffee fields. It is run by amazingly friendly woman, full of good energy and love. Super views!
Notify them in advance if you plan to come, they live nearby and will be very happy to prepare something for you! They are active on instagram @gempiniscoffee
review 3: Amazing spot with beautiful views and delicious food. Message them ahead of time to make sure someone is there. Definitely worth a visit!
review 4: Bu ngurah is the best host imaginable. This little oasis of a coffeeshop is nestled amidst her own coffee plantation, while overlooking the beautiful batu karu mountain. The pisang goreng is top notch and the coffee is sublime. Something of a hidden treasure in these parts. Just make sure to contact before coming!
review 5: Wow such a lovely secluded spot with great food, great coffee and a romantic vibe! Owners are super friendly too. Toilets are clean. Menu is vegan. Can't recommend enough.
